      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/C80lC-FxIn8/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653387519_18112873159710613_5809545089604463390_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQwMTUwNjUzODE2MTIzMTExMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=7WagNoDtzXgQ7kNvwEx3QyC&amp;_nc_oc=AdoM3PIZYEdK89-scQ-1LYjKYM2pwWwbFLWunyTM6DXrcQ9_EzSYjMeuziI3ScmB4eI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=LCsPyIwSKqUbMWSPTmMkkg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxwNctpEQllhnIrD-p9C2xhevh6y8Dhfj3DCPwVHsfZdg&amp;oe=69C8EEA1" alt="Instagram billede fra @cho_co_pie" /></p><p><strong>@cho_co_pie</strong></p><p>Americana! 🇯🇵🇺🇸 <br/>
<br/>
Idk why but I find the dualism between Japanese and American culture fascinating. The contrast between Japanese typography and “Western” imagery evokes a certain feeling I really can’t explain.. <br/>
<br/>
#graphicdesign #graphicdesigner #citypop #posters #typography #japanese</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653387519_18112873159710613_5809545089604463390_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQwMTUwNjUzODE2MTIzMTExMw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=7WagNoDtzXgQ7kNvwEx3QyC&amp;_nc_oc=AdoM3PIZYEdK89-scQ-1LYjKYM2pwWwbFLWunyTM6DXrcQ9_EzSYjMeuziI3ScmB4eI&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=LCsPyIwSKqUbMWSPTmMkkg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxwNctpEQllhnIrD-p9C2xhevh6y8Dhfj3DCPwVHsfZdg&amp;oe=69C8EEA1" alt="Instagram billede fra @cho_co_pie" /></p><p><strong>@cho_co_pie</strong></p><p>Americana! 🇯🇵🇺🇸 <br/>
<br/>
Idk why but I find the dualism between Japanese and American culture fascinating. The contrast between Japanese typography and “Western” imagery evokes a certain feeling I really can’t explain.. <br/>
<br/>
#graphicdesign #graphicdesigner #citypop #posters #typography #japanese</p>]]></content:encoded>
